The '''Guild Reform Committee''' was one of two factions that formed when [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] split the [[Bounty Hunters' Guild/Legends|Bounty Hunters' Guild]] in two. The Committee was formed out of resentment for the elder members of the order who seceded from the Guild and consequently formed their own organization, the [[True Guild]]. The Committee was headed by [[Bossk/Legends|Bossk]]. Both the Guild Reform Committee and the True Guild were eventually destroyed during the [[Bounty Hunter Wars]].

